7
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,840
Je, da, nažalost, ti je malo.

8
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:51,440
Ne radi tebe, ali.

9
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:54,080
Je, nije radi mene, malo si stišao, ali to sve je ono.

10
00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:54,960
Nažalost.

11
